1
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:56,920
Your Highness

2
00:00:58,280 --> 00:00:59,840
Thank you for your help.

3
00:01:00,679 --> 00:01:01,520
Mr. Lou

4
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:05,640
You know both of them?

5
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:08,040
I just met them once.

6
00:01:08,239 --> 00:01:09,239
We are not familiar.

7
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,719
You can disregard the danger

8
00:01:11,879 --> 00:01:13,560
and save us from the danger.

9
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,599
This kindness

10
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,799
will be repaid in the future.

11
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:17,239
No need.

12
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:20,000
We just arrived in Kyoto a few days ago.

13
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:22,079
We wanted to find a restaurant to eat,

14
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,599
but our wallet was stolen

15
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:24,760
when we were paying the bill.

16
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:26,959
Fortunately, you were generous enough to help us.

17
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,480
Thank you very much.

18
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:30,879
I just happened to pass by.

19
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:31,799
It's just a small favor.

20
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:32,879
Don't worry.

21
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,439
I didn't expect that

22
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,280
the thieves in the capital

23
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,120
are so rampant now.

24
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,200
They are lawless.

25
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,359
Although these villains have escaped,

26
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,560
it's late at night.

27
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,719
You'd better go home as soon as possible

28
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,319
in case they come back.

29
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:49,719
Madam,

30
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,920
the carriage is fixed.

31
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:55,599
Thank you.

32
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,120
Then we

33
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,400
will take our leave.

34
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,000
Take your leave?

35
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:01,480
You...

36
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,599
You're injured.

37
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,120
It's just a minor wound.

38
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:05,719
It's nothing.

39
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:07,799
If it weren't for saving us,

40
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,199
you wouldn't have been hurt.

41
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,960
We have some medicine in the carriage.

42
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,520
Why don't you come with me

43
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,639
and treat it before leaving?

44
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,199
Yeah, yeah.

45
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:17,159
You...

46
00:02:17,479 --> 00:02:18,439
You're still bleeding.

47
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,719
Stop bleeding is a priority.

48
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:29,599
If you don't take off your clothes,

49
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,919
how can I apply medicine for you?

50
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:35,159
Princess Consort of Rui treats a stranger.

51
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,159
If it is spread out,

52
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,560
you will be criticized.

53
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,520
All outside are my confidants.

54
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,639
so no one will spread it.

55
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,120
Unless

56
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:46,479
you want to tell others.

57
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:48,560
If you don't mind,

58
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:49,759
thank you.

59
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,800
How did you get so many scars

60
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:04,080
if you don't fight with others?

61
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,759
I saw you

62
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,159
fighting against the bandits.

63
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,759
You're very agile.

64
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,159
You drove them away

65
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,479
in just two moves.

66
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,479
You must be skilled in martial arts.

67
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,479
My brother and I

68
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:20,159
travel for business,

69
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,879
so we often encounter bandits.

70
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,039
Over time,

71
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:25,039
we've learned some self-defense.

72
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,120
But you,

73
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,000
remained calm in the face of danger.

74
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:30,879
Did you anticipate this?

75
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,879
You must be joking.

76
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:34,840
I'm just a weak woman.

77
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,759
How could I possibly be connected to bandits?

78
00:03:39,879 --> 00:03:41,159
Ordinary bandits

79
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,439
only seek wealth.

80
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,680
Rarely do they take lives.

81
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,479
The thugs just now were ruthless.

82
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:48,759
It seemed more like revenge.

83
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:50,639
Have you recently

84
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,759
offended someone?

85
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:55,039
Those thugs

86
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,439
are just ordinary bandits.

87
00:03:58,599 --> 00:03:59,680
You speculate like this.

88
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,080
Did you find any clues?

89
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:03,960
Just guessing.

90
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:06,800
I heard

91
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:08,240
that it is said in the capital

92
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:10,560
that Minister Shen and Prince Rui are not in harmony.

93
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:11,719
But today

94
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,719
you suddenly became in-laws.

95
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:16,399
It's hard not to arouse jealousy.

96
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,600
You're quite knowledgeable about court affairs.

97
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,040
It's just some rumors.

98
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,439
I'm not knowledgeable.

99
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,319
Alright.

100
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,439
Are you

101
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,399
just passing by?

102
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:43,399
I really

103
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,839
don't know what happened tonight.

104
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,360
There are many people

105
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,480
in Lingguo Temple today.

106
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,439
There are over a hundred guards with swords.

107
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:56,639
You were invited to pray,

108
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,079
but you brought so many guards,

109
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,600
most of them are martial artists.

110
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:01,959
Does Your Highness

111
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:04,199
not trust the imperial guards?

112
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,360
Or are you aware of

113
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,279
tonight's events?

114
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:15,199
If Your Highness is willing to tell the truth,

115
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,199
I will

116
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,720
do the same.

117
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:20,879
My Lord,

118
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:23,439
Someone suddenly intervened and saved Lady Shen.

119
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,319
I was worried about exposing our identities,

120
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,879
so I had to retreat.

121
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:30,800
Do you know

122
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,560
who they are?

123
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:34,399
I have never seen them before,

124
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:36,120
but judging by their skills,

125
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,959
they don't seem to be ordinary people.

126
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,000
And they seem to be

127
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:41,160
acquaintances of the princess.

128
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,839
Old acquaintances?

129
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,160
Take care of those dead bodies.

130
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:48,759
Leave no trace.

131
00:05:49,759 --> 00:05:50,480
As for the rest,

132
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:51,920
I'll make further arrangements.

133
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:53,120
Yes.

134
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,360
Those bandits

135
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,120
dared to act so brazenly

136
00:06:08,639 --> 00:06:10,279
in the Emperor's territory.

137
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,800
It's truly frightening to think about.

138
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:14,199
Sui'er,

139
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,000
You must

140
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,879
never be as reckless

141
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,160
as you were today,

142
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,120
placing yourself in front of me.

143
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,079
If something had happened to you,

144
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,199
I wouldn't know what to do.

145
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,319
Mother,

146
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,480
no matter what happens,

147
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,600
I will always protect you.

148
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:34,319
Your Highness,

149
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,040
The men

150
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,680
were agile and ruthless.

151
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,480
They're not ordinary bandits,

152
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,120
but well-trained killers.

153
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,319
If you hadn't noticed them

154
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,040
and escorted them,

155
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,360
they

156
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:48,759
would have been killed.

157
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,079
Your Highness,

158
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:54,600
did you meet the Imperial Consort Dowager?

159
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:56,160
You came back without permission.

160
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,040
Did she blame you?

161
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,560
That's the Prime Minister's carriage.

162
00:06:59,439 --> 00:07:00,519
It's Princess Consort of Rui and Lady Shen.

163
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,000
Today is the fifteenth day of the lunar month.

164
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,959
It should be the Empress's invitation

165
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,079
to pray for blessings at Lingguo Temple.

166
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:06,959
But

167
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,279
Princess Consort of Rui is too pretentious.

168
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,399
She brought so many people to pray.

169
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,560
If I don't know,

170
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,680
she is a concubine of the Emperor.

171
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,199
So ostentatious.

172
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,879
It's not like her.

173
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:20,439
By the way, Your Highness.

174
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,720
While waiting for you,

175
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:23,839
I saw someone

176
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,439
wandering around the carriage of the PM's Residence.

177
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:26,920
It seems that

178
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,959
he did something.

179
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,199
But

180
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,360
they brought so many people,

181
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,600
there shouldn't be any problem.

182
00:07:34,319 --> 00:07:34,680
Back to the city.

183
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,120
Your Highness,

184
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:37,480
don't we have something to do?

185
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:39,879
Dare to do such a thing in Kyoto,

186
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,920
the person behind it is definitely not simple.

187
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,480
But if the princess

188
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,800
indeed expected

189
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,040
what happened tonight,

190
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,399
then what is she hiding?

191
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,480
[Princess Consort of Rui,]

192
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:57,360
[what secrets are you hiding?]

193
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,120
You've troubled yourself over this.

194
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,480
I'm just a bit shaken up.

195
00:08:02,959 --> 00:08:05,000
No need to bother the royal physician.

196
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,319
I should have sent a team of guards

197
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:08,079
to escort you back.

198
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,800
Those thugs wouldn't have dared

199
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:12,040
to act if they saw royal guards.

200
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,000
It's my fault for

201
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:14,800
not considering this.

202
00:08:15,639 --> 00:08:17,120
You're still as thoughtful

203
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,120
as when you were a child.

204
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,399
I was just unlucky.

205
00:08:20,959 --> 00:08:21,959
I ran into a few bandits

206
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,600
on the way back to the city.

207
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,600
Fortunately, there was no danger.

208
00:08:27,079 --> 00:08:27,639
This matter

209
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,639
is not your fault.

210
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,480
Mother,

211
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:32,519
Zhao is just worried about your health.

212
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,080
Just let him have his way.

213
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,080
Okay.

214
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:37,960
By the way, Zhao,

215
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,840
have those bandits been caught?

216
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,879
I've urged the authorities

217
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:42,960
to apprehend

218
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,399
the perpetrators as soon as possible.

219
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,320
We should have results soon.

220
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,080
Sir,

221
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:51,639
I have some questions

222
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:52,840
I'd like to ask you.

223
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,519
Doctor Liu,

224
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,399
this way.

225
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,320
Your Highness,

226
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:02,360
please allow me to check your pulse.

227
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:08,759
Your Highness,

228
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:09,759
please.

229
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:15,919
To be honest,

230
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:17,159
on my way here,

231
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,519
I went to the government office.

232
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,320
Those bandits

233
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:22,279
were found dead in the wilderness this morning.

234
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:23,919
Judging by the scene,

235
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:25,799
it seems they died

236
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,519
due to a fight over uneven distribution of loot.

237
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,159
But from what I know,

238
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,320
when they attacked your wife and Sui'er,

239
00:09:31,759 --> 00:09:33,000
they didn't demand any money.

240
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:34,799
Do you also think

241
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:35,799
this

242
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,639
was just a coincidence?

243
00:09:41,639 --> 00:09:42,279
Your silence

244
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:44,000
must mean you already have an answer in mind.

245
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:45,519
You just

246
00:09:46,039 --> 00:09:46,879
don't want to say it.

247
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,120
I don't like the court politics,

248
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,120
but I know my brother

249
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:52,039
quite well.

250
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:53,840
He has been longing for

251
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:54,799
the Crown Prince.

252
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,879
But you always

253
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,159
argue with him in front of our father,

254
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,960
which makes him feel embarrassed.

255
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:03,679
Now,

256
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,480
His Majesty is forcing him to marry Sui'er.

257
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:07,759
I'm worried

258
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:08,960
he might

259
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,440
take drastic actions.

260
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,559
He may be reckless,

261
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,639
but he shouldn't

262
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:19,960
be so cruel.

263
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:21,159
I will

264
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:22,919
consider this carefully.

265
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:24,200
Master.

266
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:24,600
Dad.

267
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:26,679
Zhao.

268
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:28,000
We all saw it.

269
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:29,799
Minister Shen.

270
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:33,600
I just checked both the madam and the princess consort.

271
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,759
The princess consort is just frightened,

272
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:36,720
but she's fine.

273
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,120
But the madam's pulse is weak,

274
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:42,639
which may be caused by her usual fatigue,

275
00:10:43,399 --> 00:10:44,440
plus the fright.

276
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:46,679
Although she looks fine now,

277
00:10:47,039 --> 00:10:47,559
but

278
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:48,519
she's sick inside.

279
00:10:48,919 --> 00:10:49,919
If not treated in time,

280
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:51,840
it may turn into a serious illness.

281
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,000
Dr. Liu,

282
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:55,480
do you have a good idea?

283
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:58,000
Although this illness cannot be cured in a hurry,

284
00:10:58,639 --> 00:11:00,000
I have been treating her

285
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,559
every day in recent days.

286
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,440
Thank you, Dr. Liu.

287
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:06,720
Master,

288
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,799
don't worry too much.

289
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,440
Doctor Liu is skilled.

290
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:10,840
Your wife will be fine.

291
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,720
I'll see him off.

292
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,120
I'll come to see you later.

293
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:18,840
Okay.

294
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:30,600
Dad,

295
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,679
I'll see them off.

296
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:32,519
Okay.

297
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,080
Zhao,

298
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,120
Sui'er,

299
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,120
is there anything you want to tell me?

300
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,879
Zhao, you don't have to hide it from me.

301
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,159
Those people yesterday

302
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,440
were not ordinary thieves,

303
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:55,879
right?

304
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,840
Did the government really find nothing?

305
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,440
My mother and I were attacked last night.

306
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:03,080
Is it related to the Second Prince?

307
00:12:06,039 --> 00:12:06,840
Actually,

308
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,960
they have found something,

309
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,159
but they dare not investigate further.

310
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:12,080
So they had to close the case.

311
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:13,960
Those people

312
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:15,320
are not ordinary thieves,

313
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:16,200
but are suicide bombers.

314
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:18,840
And my brother

315
00:12:19,039 --> 00:12:20,399
raised suicide bombers privately.

316
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,080
Everyone in the imperial court knows it,

317
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,639
but no one dares to report it.

318
00:12:24,399 --> 00:12:25,600
I shouldn't have told you this,

319
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,360
but you are in Prince Rui's Mansion.

320
00:12:29,519 --> 00:12:30,480
If it's really him,

321
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:32,440
you must be more careful.

322
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,679
Mu Jinghao

323
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,559
was attacked last night.

324
00:12:36,039 --> 00:12:37,279
It was really you.

325
00:12:39,919 --> 00:12:41,240
Thank you for telling me the truth.

326
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:42,639
I know what to do.

327
00:12:48,919 --> 00:12:50,759
Although I can't stop your marriage,

328
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,320
I will try my best

329
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,919
I'll do my best to help.

330
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:56,639
Your Highness,

331
00:12:58,039 --> 00:13:00,279
Doctor Liu has replaced the previous one

332
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,120
and entered the Prime Minister's Residence.

333
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:04,360
He will help Lady Shen recover every day.

334
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,320
If it works,

335
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:08,279
you can take down Prime Minister Shen.

336
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,120
If not,

337
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:12,039
even if something goes wrong,

338
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:15,120
he was recommended by Prince IV.

339
00:13:15,519 --> 00:13:17,120
You won't be implicated.

340
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:18,879
Shu Wuqi,

341
00:13:19,639 --> 00:13:20,720
thanks to your ingenuity,

342
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,039
you've come up with such a perfect plan.

343
00:13:32,879 --> 00:13:33,360
Take it.

344
00:13:33,639 --> 00:13:34,159
Thank you.

345
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:51,480
Your Highness,

346
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,080
our men at the border

347
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,080
reported they spotted General Xiao,

348
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,039
heading north.

349
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:57,559
This was found by our people.

350
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:58,399
Please take a look.

351
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,759
is this something he left behind?

352
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,039
My brother,

353
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:04,679
you're leading a team into the camp tonight.

354
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:05,919
You must be extremely careful.

355
00:14:06,679 --> 00:14:07,639
If anything goes wrong,

356
00:14:07,919 --> 00:14:08,799
you must retreat safely.

357
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,360
Your life is more important.

358
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:11,720
We can always

359
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,200
come up with another plan.

360
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,320
Don't worry.

361
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:15,600
I'm a veteran of many battles.

362
00:14:15,799 --> 00:14:16,759
I know what to do.

363
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:17,919
I'll be fine.

364
00:14:18,799 --> 00:14:19,360
I'll

365
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:21,000
leave marks along the way.

366
00:14:21,759 --> 00:14:22,600
You can follow them

367
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:24,320
and attack up.

368
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:29,159
Be careful.

369
00:14:34,279 --> 00:14:34,960
It's General Xiao!

370
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,440
Great!

371
00:14:36,879 --> 00:14:38,200
General Xiao is blessed by God,

372
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,120
he's still alive.

373
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:40,720
Send more people

374
00:14:41,039 --> 00:14:41,639
to find him.

375
00:14:41,799 --> 00:14:42,039
Yes.

376
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:45,080
Prince.

377
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:46,360
They are

378
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:48,200
Lady Shen and Princess Consort Rui.

379
00:14:49,879 --> 00:14:51,240
They're wandering at night.

380
00:14:51,799 --> 00:14:52,399
It seems

381
00:14:53,039 --> 00:14:54,960
Lady Shen's condition has improved.

382
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:56,279
Sui'er,

383
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,799
you've just got married.

384
00:14:59,559 --> 00:15:01,159
You shouldn't stay at your parents' house.

385
00:15:02,039 --> 00:15:03,360
If you stay here too long,

386
00:15:03,879 --> 00:15:04,519
I'm afraid

387
00:15:04,679 --> 00:15:06,080
His Highness will be unhappy.

388
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,399
It's time

389
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:09,279
to go back to his mansion.

390
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:11,639
He has Ling Chuchu by his side.

391
00:15:11,919 --> 00:15:13,039
He doesn't want me to go back.

392
00:15:13,519 --> 00:15:14,200
Besides,

393
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:16,399
I've never been away from my mom.

394
00:15:16,879 --> 00:15:17,879
It's hard for me

395
00:15:18,399 --> 00:15:20,000
to adapt to the new life.

396
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:23,080
You are

397
00:15:23,759 --> 00:15:24,840
such a spoiled girl.

398
00:15:26,919 --> 00:15:27,480
Mom,

399
00:15:27,639 --> 00:15:28,399
what's wrong with you?

400
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:30,399
Doctor Liu comes to the mansion every day

401
00:15:30,399 --> 00:15:31,440
to help you recover.

402
00:15:31,919 --> 00:15:32,759
But you look

403
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,679
worse than before.

404
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,279
I'm fine.

405
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:43,399
How about

406
00:15:44,039 --> 00:15:45,240
going back to your hometown

407
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,440
for a few days?

408
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:47,799
A change of environment

409
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:48,679
may

410
00:15:48,879 --> 00:15:50,039
be good for your health.

411
00:15:50,919 --> 00:15:52,399
[If I can get her out of Kyoto,]

412
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,399
[she won't be in danger anymore.]

413
00:15:55,039 --> 00:15:56,919
You didn't want me to leave just now.

414
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:57,480
But

415
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,200
you're sending me away so soon?

416
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,879
Mother,

417
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:03,039
you know I didn't mean that.

418
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:03,320
By the way,

419
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:04,960
any updates on those

420
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:05,799
bandits I asked you to look into?

421
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:07,519
The ones who attacked Princess Consort Rui

422
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,519
weren't ordinary bandits,

423
00:16:09,039 --> 00:16:09,559
but

424
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,679
trained killers.

425
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,480
They left no clues.

426
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:13,600
But

427
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:15,759
someone has been watching

428
00:16:15,759 --> 00:16:16,519
the PM's Mansion recently.

429
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:17,919
Is it Prince Rui's man?

430
00:16:19,519 --> 00:16:20,159
Sui'er, look.

431
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,039
Lanterns.

432
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:23,120
Do you remember?

433
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:24,399
When you were a child,

434
00:16:24,799 --> 00:16:26,080
you liked lanterns.

435
00:16:26,679 --> 00:16:27,799
You always asked me

436
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,639
to make one for you.

437
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,200
Now,

438
00:16:31,879 --> 00:16:33,159
I'll make one for you.

439
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:36,960
Great.

440
00:16:41,799 --> 00:16:42,320
Mom,

441
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:43,600
wait for me.

442
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:46,480
Miss,

443
00:16:59,440 --> 00:16:59,960
I want this one.

444
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,519
20 wen.

445
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,639
Wish you

446
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:04,839
a good marriage.

447
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:07,640
I don't need a good match,

448
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,000
just peace.

449
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:11,559
I'll take this.

450
00:17:11,839 --> 00:17:12,960
I saw it first.

451
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:13,319
You?

452
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:18,440
How come it's you?

453
00:17:19,359 --> 00:17:19,839
Princess Consort,

454
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:21,200
long time no see.

455
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:23,880
Young Master Lou,

456
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:25,799
is tonight's encounter

457
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:27,079
also just a coincidence?

458
00:17:28,079 --> 00:17:28,880
If I say

459
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,279
I just happened to pass by,

460
00:17:30,279 --> 00:17:30,720
would you believe me?

461
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:31,799
If I don't believe you,

462
00:17:32,359 --> 00:17:33,319
will you tell me the truth?

463
00:17:34,279 --> 00:17:35,279
Why did you bring so many tails

464
00:17:35,559 --> 00:17:36,839
when you go out?

465
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:39,759
No need to look.

466
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:41,400
I've already dealt with them.

467
00:17:45,039 --> 00:17:46,240
How did you know someone was following me?

468
00:17:47,359 --> 00:17:48,160
Or

469
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:50,200
are you one of the tails?

470
00:17:53,119 --> 00:17:53,759
Someone fainted.

471
00:17:58,240 --> 00:17:58,799
Mother.
